.TH KINGPEPE-TX 1
.SH NAME
kingpepe-tx \- KingPepe Core transaction utility
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kingpepe-tx
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fICOMMANDS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B kingpepe-tx
tool creates and modifies serialized KingPepe transactions without requiring a
running node.
.SH OPTIONS
Run
.B kingpepe-tx -help
for the complete option list supported by this build.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kingpepe-cli (1)
